and we hope you’ll also be.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/3clicks-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/5092225\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase 3Clicks theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">Royal theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://www.8theme.com/shop/wordpress/royal-wordpress-theme/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/royal.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>We are a team of designers and developers that create high quality Magento and WordPress themes and provide premium and dedicated support to our products.Enhance your websites with our royal designs. Our premium Magento templates give your online presence the edge it needs.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://www.8theme.com/shop/wordpress/royal-wordpress-theme/\">Purchase Royal theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">WooCommerce Plivo SMS notifications<br />\n</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-plivo/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/pilvo.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>This Plivo plugin for WordPress WooCommerce makes sending SMS status notifications easy. Your customers will love it.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-plivo/\">Download WooCommerce Plivo SMS notifications</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=ydCec2P1maM:blh0vP-sczk:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=ydCec2P1maM:blh0vP-sczk:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"ht