>Glass pool walls</a>: underwater glazing, bubble windows.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"/illuminator-v-basseyne/?lang=en\">Round viewing windows (portholes)</a>, underwater pool windows.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"/osteklenie-dna-basseyna/?lang=en\">Glass pool bottom</a>, underwater bottom glazing, framework structure window in the pool bottom.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"/steklannoe-jakyzi-v-interyere-baseyna/?lang=en\">Glass hot tub</a>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Now, your swimming pool is not just a basin in the ground. You can design the pool and the space around it in three dimensions. With the help of modern technologies, it is possible to glaze the pool walls or make them higher, to make a transparent bottom or separate hot tub area and pool area harmoniously. Time slows down in such a pool! Proven German technologies that we use increase the attractiveness of your pool tenfold, whether it is a private or a public swimming pool at a sports club or a beauty spa.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Beyond any doubt, we can construct whatever you might think of. A simple pencil drawing of yours is enough to fix a budget and to determine feasibility and the construction period. We are sure to find the best resolution for to make your idea come true. Design and construction of swimming pools is what we are good at!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Contact our designer and they will help you to create a pool of your dream.</p>\r\n&nbsp;','Transparent swimming pool','','publish','open','open','','transparent_pool','','','2014-10-10 10:13:19','2014-10-10 06:13:19','',0,'http://poolglass.ru/?page_id=1148',0,'page','',0),(1149,1,'2014-08-13 15:32:11','2014-08-13 11:32:11','---','Prices and Promotions','','publish','open','open','','cenu-i-akcii','','','2014-09-03 11:31:38','2014-09-03 07:31:38','',0,'http://poolglass.ru/?page_id=1149',0,'page','',0),(1150